<div class="sd2-blue__faq sd2-faqs__list"><details open><summary>Where is Sinister Diesel located?</summary><p>Sinister Diesel is based in Roseville, California, east of Sacramento. Orders may ship from different fulfillment locations.</p></details><details><summary>When will my order arrive?</summary><p>Processing time, product availability, destination and the selected carrier service all affect delivery. Transit estimates begin after carrier pickup. Review the <a href="shipping-policies.html">Shipping Policies</a> and use <a href="help-check-order-status.html">Order Tracking</a> for current order information.</p></details><details><summary>What is a core charge?</summary><p>A core charge is a refundable amount associated with selected remanufactured parts. Eligibility depends on returning an acceptable old component within the applicable time. Review the <a href="core-returns.html">Core Returns guide</a>.</p></details><details><summary>Is there a warranty on parts?</summary><p>Coverage varies by brand and product. Review the <a href="warranty-information.html">Warranty Policy</a> and submit a <a href="help-warranty-inquiry.html">Warranty Inquiry</a> when you need help with a specific item.</p></details><details><summary>How can I become a dealer?</summary><p>Use the <a href="dealer-application.html">Dealer Application</a> to provide your business information for review.</p></details><details><summary>Do you accept returns?</summary><p>Return eligibility depends on the item, condition and timing. Review the <a href="return-and-warranty-policies.html">Returns and Exchanges policy</a> before sending a product back.</p></details><details><summary>Can I request pricing or a package recommendation?</summary><p>Contact the <a href="help-sales-inquiry.html">Sales team</a> with your truck year, engine, use case and desired parts. Current pricing and promotions are subject to their published terms.</p></details><details><summary>Where can I find installation information?</summary><p>Start with the <a href="install-hub.html">Install Hub</a>, then search the <a href="install-instructions.html">Install Instructions library</a> using the exact product code.</p></details></div>
